            <Title>She’s leaving home</Title>
            <Text>She’s leaving home
Traveller’s Perch
Adno continues her reconnaissance of Hanikori. She discovers that Tanoch was right. He is planning an accident that will kill Diver and FF. She tells them and about the spaceship that can bring them to her homeworld. She will join them there later, but they will be safe there. They agree but don’t want to steal it — they don’t want to be always on the run. Instead they announce they are retiring to have a baby and the volunteer to test pilot the ship to Water Eye to help Putnomo out. Hanikori grudgingly lets them go, hoping they’ll die enroute, since the technology is not that great. But Adno uses the school to troubleshoot and they secretely improve it so that they can make the journey safely.</Text>
